# ===========================================================
# Becoming Famous - .gitignore
# ONLY the site/ folder + root index.html (redirect) are
# pushed to GitHub. Everything else (megadocs, MD reference
# files, Python scripts, bats, source PDFs) stays local.
# ===========================================================

# Ignore everything in this folder by default
*

# But keep these:
!.gitignore
!index.html
!site/
!site/**
